  • public class ContactInfoBook
extends java.lang.Object
    To implement and create a contact information book in which stores the data inputed From a user, into a contact listed text file. This Contact Information Book is for a more business oriented piece of application To store in the details of a contact/client to therefore get hold of for future use/projects/queries George Sulaiman i7437472 Programming Assignment 28/04/2016
